<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Donauwörth</head><p>Der Rat teilt mit, dass er wegen Vertretung beim Landfrieden keine Ratsherren zum Tag nach Augsburg entsenden kann.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_48" id="23v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_48_r1l1">Werde / </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_48_r1l2"><expan>Lıeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> frewnde / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd gepeten habt / daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_48_r1l3">vvir ew cʒwen <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> Rates <expan>leıh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>ſchıcke<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ſolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / daʒ die auf </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_48_r1l6">den nehſten Pfıncʒtag bey 
<del rend="strikethrough">ew </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_48_r1l4">den ewren </ab></add> cʒü <expan>Augſp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> <expan>w<ex>er</ex>en</expan> / als Jr <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_48_r1l7">doſelbſt mit den von Vlme <expan>cʒeſchicke<ex>n</ex></expan> habt / Laſſen wir ewr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_48_r1l8">frewntſchaft wiſſen / daʒ vvir von nötlıcher ſache <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_48_r1l9">vnſer 
<del rend="strikethrough">bot </del> erber botſchefte / beıde cʒü dem Lantfrid vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_48_r1l10"><expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> enden / ſchıcken vnd <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> müſſen / des wır vns alles </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_48_r1l12">vorhin <expan>vervange<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_48_line_1572978372901_39"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab></add> / . Alſo / daʒ wir alſpalde <expan>nyema<ex>n</ex>t</expan> <expan>gehab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_48_r1l13">mügen / den wir ew ſchıcken der ew dar cʒü nücʒe wer / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_48_r1l14">vnd <expan>bitt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd getrawen <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> erberkeit vvol / daʒ Jr vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_48_r1l15">das nicht für v̈bel <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet / vvan wo wır ew lieb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_48_r1l16">vnd fruntſchaft <expan>beweiſe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>möht<ex>en</ex></expan> / das <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>allcʒ<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_48_r1l17"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>Sab<ex>at</ex>o</expan> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Martinj . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_48" id="23v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Werde </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> frewnde, als ir uns
                                                  <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                                                gepeten habt, daz wir ew czwen
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> rates
                                                  <expan>leih<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                                                  <expan>schicke<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>solt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz die auf den
                                          <app><note><q type="date">nehsten pfincztag</q>14.11.1409</note></app> bey <add>den ewren</add> czü
                                                  <expan>Augsp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>en</expan>, als ir
                                                  <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> doselbst mit den von
                                                Ulme <expan>czeschicke<ex>n</ex></expan> habt,
                                                lassen wir ewr frewntschaft wissen, daz wir von
                                                nötlicher sache <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> unser
                                                erber botschefte beide czü dem lantfrid und
                                                  <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> enden schicken und
                                                  <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> müssen, des wir uns
                                                alles vorhin <expan>vervange<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan></add>. Also daz
                                                wir alspalde <expan>nyema<ex>n</ex>t</expan>
<expan>gehab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mügen, den wir ew
                                                schicken, der ew dar czü nücze wer; und
                                                  <expan>bitt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und getrawen
                                                  <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> erberkeit wol, daz
                                                ir uns das nicht für übel
                                                  <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet. Wan wo wir
                                                ew lieb und fruntschaft
                                                  <expan>beweise<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>möht<ex>en</ex></expan>, das
                                                  <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                                  <expan>allcz<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sab<ex>at</ex>o</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Martini. </ab>
</div>
